{"tid":1933608,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"Agile working (坐豬肉枱）真係遲早令員工攬炒，齊齊中武肺","createTime":"2020-03-19T11:24:07.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-21T16:33:46.000Z","uid":4798,"like":37,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"7c943ede23224a751330fcc980733b2edd66fa20","tid":1933608,"uid":4798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T11:24:07.000Z","msg":"今次疫症真係令啲乜撚agile working嘅弊處現哂型！<br />\n唔知大家做邊行啦，不過好多外資／大公司以家都好興行Agile working，<br />\n姐係每個員工唔會再有固定嘅枱，而係每日番工爭凳仔坐。<br />\n<br />\n本身疫症前已經唔算好work，<br />\n因為我條team成日都要去見客，所以基本上大家輪流出左去開會，<br />\n啲位都尚且夠坐，咁岩某一兩日多人啲就要坐個啲collaboration area。<br />\n問題黎啦，家下疫情嚴重，其實我自己唔少客都仲係行緊Work from home 或者唔比Visitor入佢地公司，所以好多同事都係用電話/Zoom開會。<br />\n結果個撚個都因為開會轉左做Conf. call而番左office，結果無固定位嘅後果就係要爭凳仔，遲左少少番就要坐去啲collaboration area，家下嚴重到呢D位都坐爆哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n仲要本身啲workstation與workstation之間係無棟塊partition，結果同四周圍啲同事都有親密接觸（係office啲人都唔撚帶罩），比豬肉枱更豬肉枱嘅collaboration area仲迫過係澳牛食飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n屌你老味然後公司當睇唔到，唔知道唔理會唔正視，仲要家下經濟差，個個驚炒人又唔敢出聲，optional work from home都唔敢request。<br />\n<br />\n說到底，agile working咪就係包裝公司想慳租嘅真相姐嘛。喂你想慳租我明白，但以家呢啲緊急狀態，你又唔撚叫人work from home，又唔撚正視office根本唔夠位坐同埋張枱污糟過公廁嘅問題，係咪想有一個人奶野嘅時候，要全公司一齊攬炒呀？屌你老母呀真係<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ba72f7ed93b8158219b59727ffa9920c3755578","tid":1933608,"uid":125168,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T11:30:02.000Z","msg":"唯有噴多d酒精"},{"pid":"769ccd63663345673c3799dbeebbb50b33db01a7","tid":1933608,"uid":4798,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"quote":{"pid":"3ba72f7ed93b8158219b59727ffa9920c3755578","tid":1933608,"uid":125168,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T11:30:02.000Z","msg":"唯有噴多d酒精"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T11:32:29.000Z","msg":"噴乜撚都無用，個撚個覺得係office 就唔洗戴罩，<br />\n仲要迫撚到仆街，留名睇攬炒"},{"pid":"7c08255af28f129f83edd2123ab03a701e32cf98","tid":1933608,"uid":4798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T11:32:42.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4449b9a8ebef8e7604f5bf0267559ace743d59a9","tid":1933608,"uid":125168,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"769ccd63663345673c3799dbeebbb50b33db01a7","tid":1933608,"uid":4798,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"quote":{"pid":"3ba72f7ed93b8158219b59727ffa9920c3755578","tid":1933608,"uid":125168,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T11:30:02.000Z","msg":"唯有噴多d酒精"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T11:32:29.000Z","msg":"噴乜撚都無用，個撚個覺得係office 就唔洗戴罩，<br />\n仲要迫撚到仆街，留名睇攬炒"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T11:33:24.000Z","msg":"原來佢哋罩都唔戴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\